Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.71,0:03:08.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The Eight-Six is right on his tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:11.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:13.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakazato is fighting so desperately!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.82,0:03:15.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.95,0:03:41.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!  That's the braking\Ndrift of the Eight-Six!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.10,0:03:45.39,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.69,0:03:53.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The FC...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:54.56,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi Ryosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.07,0:04:00.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I watched Keisuke being overtaken by\Nthe Eight-Six in these five hairpins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.99,0:04:05.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}That Eight-Six used\Nthe gutter to turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.79,0:04:11.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He blocked the inside.  He's trying\Nnot to let him squeeze in!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.26,0:04:13.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That Nakazato...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:16.67,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}What're you going to do, Eight-Six?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.79,0:04:29.31,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What?\NFrom the outside?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:38.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:39.11,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I...it's gonna crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.81,0:04:47.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't screw around with me!\NI won't let you pass from the outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:04:58.46,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like the 32.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:05:00.96,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Sharp acceleration at the exit is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.96,0:05:03.21,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, that Eight-Six...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.21,0:05:06.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He kept skidding in such\Na narrow curve.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.52,0:05:08.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Three more corners...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:11.14,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...and this battle will be settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:27.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to overtake from\Nthe outside again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.87,0:05:33.11,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So frustrating!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.11,0:05:36.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It pisses me off when\Nhe gets outside of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.05,0:05:49.41,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The 32 is acting strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.41,0:05:52.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakazato has lost his concentration.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.23,0:05:54.11,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your eyes on them, Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.11,0:05:55.97,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The Eight-Six's gonna overtake him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.15,0:05:58.93,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Overtake him...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.93,0:06:01.01,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But the inside is blocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.41,0:06:04.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.35,0:06:07.66,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi's trying to overtake him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.66,0:06:08.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.20,0:06:11.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:13.86,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Takumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.75,0:06:25.19,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I'm humiliated in front of so many galleries,\Nalmost being overtaken from the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.19,0:06:27.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Because I get too close\Nto the inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.00,0:06:29.86,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}...the car misses the ideal line, and the\Nentry speed has to be slower!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:34.77,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}That's right.  I only have to make a space\Nslightly narrower than a car!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.77,0:06:37.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}That way, my entry speed can be faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.14,0:06:46.46,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Good, he's not gonna take the inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:09.45,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The Eight-Six disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.90,0:07:12.92,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}It can't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.14,0:07:27.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Dammit, it understeered\Nat a critical moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.92,0:07:36.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}He tried to go outside, and then he\Nchanged the line while braking!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.34,0:07:39.67,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The Eight-Six is capable of doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.67,0:07:42.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}But don't think that you're going to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:46.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}If we accelerate side by side, I'll be able\Nto pull ahead at full throttle in 2nd gear!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.99,0:07:50.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I'll show you the true\Npotential of the 32!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:19.97,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.86,0:08:24.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The 32 and I have lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.07,0:08:29.92,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}No, that's not right.\NOnly I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.92,0:08:33.05,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The car didn't lose to the Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.59,0:08:41.76,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}An incredible Road Racer like him exists...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.90,0:08:53.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}It's shocking, but I feel refreshed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.10,0:08:56.46,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Although I lost, I tried my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:09:00.21,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.21,0:09:03.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The bodywork will cost 70,000 yen ($700).
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:09.05,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll train myself and challenge him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:15.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it!\NTakumi won!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.68,0:09:19.69,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it!  He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.69,0:09:21.19,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.19,0:09:23.83,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi did... Takumi did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.61,0:09:25.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,N...no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.89,0:09:29.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The Eight-Six overtook the 32 in the\Nfourth corner of the five hairpins!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:32.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How could the Eight-Six defeat the 32?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.92,0:09:43.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The Eight-Six did?\NReally?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.32,0:09:44.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.84,0:09:48.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}It's just like you said, Bunta.\NJust like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:58.14,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun to watch interesting\Nthings, isn't it, Keisuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.14,0:10:02.77,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the attack of the\NEight-Six was incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.38,0:10:08.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He pretended to go outside, but changed\Nthe line during full braking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.78,0:10:14.16,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got wonderful ABS.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.06,0:10:16.46,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.46,0:10:18.21,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be dumb, Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.21,0:10:21.96,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How could an Eight-Six\Nbe equipped with ABS?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.96,0:10:23.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:25.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That was human ABS.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.19,0:10:31.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Those Road Racers who've gotten used\Nto modern cars equipped with ABS...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.53,0:10:36.81,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...would never be able to master severe pedal\Ncontrol just before locking their tires.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:45.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,ABS is computer controlled, so it can't surpass\Nthe right foot of a well-trained driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.86,0:10:49.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm finally excited after such a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.61,0:10:55.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That Eight-Six is definitely\Nworth defeating.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:29.86,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you standing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.06,0:11:32.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.55,0:11:38.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.20,0:11:39.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...about this car...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.23,0:11:46.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.53,0:11:52.31,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright.\NIt's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.63,0:11:56.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.71,0:12:31.72,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought an Eight-Six!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.72,0:12:35.13,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I kept it secret, but it was delivered today!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.71,0:12:37.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still clean!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.08,0:12:41.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So you begged your dad,\Nand made him a guarantor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.06,0:12:47.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The shop was nice, and I got a good\Nprice for the condition of the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.94,0:12:52.26,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks really good!\NIt could be a find.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.82,0:12:55.45,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.45,0:12:57.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You really bought one, Itsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.78,0:12:59.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, Takumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.55,0:13:02.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let you get too far ahead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:07.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, I'll try to be one of the two\Nfastest Eight-Six downhill Road Racers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.29,0:13:09.96,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a big talker.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.43,0:13:15.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't sleep last night\Nbecause I was so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:17.72,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.72,0:13:21.66,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't sleep the night before\Nmy S13 was delivered.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.66,0:13:25.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.\NIt's really my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.89,0:13:26.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,My car.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.94,0:13:29.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I'm having a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.82,0:13:35.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Normal wheels and 70 aspect ratio\Ntires look pathetic but adequate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.22,0:13:38.12,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, start up the engine, Itsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.12,0:13:40.12,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.  No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.01,0:13:53.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't sound so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.28,0:13:56.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's because the muffler is normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.80,0:13:59.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.\NI'll change the muffler.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.91,0:14:04.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make it sound\Nas good as Takumi's Trueno.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.17,0:14:11.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a bad feeling.\NPop the hood, Itsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.53,0:14:29.27,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.27,0:14:31.01,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Manager...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:33.71,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're mistaken, Itsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.71,0:14:35.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Mistaken...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.80,0:14:37.48,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't an Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.65,0:14:40.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an Eight-Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.22,0:14:42.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Eight-Five...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:45.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean an AE85?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.30,0:14:56.27,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Comparing the Eight-Six and Eight-Five,\Nthe body is the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.27,0:15:00.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...but the performance differences are like chocolate\Nand shit, a goddess and an old maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.74,0:15:06.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The Eight-Six has a double overhead cam engine,\Nand the Eight-Five has a single one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:10.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,DOHC and SOHC are totally different!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.42,0:15:12.92,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You bought a car without knowing that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.92,0:15:14.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.47,0:15:22.38,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry, Itsuki,\Nbut it's so funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.42,0:15:31.67,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Itsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:40.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys laughed too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:42.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Think how Itsuki feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.20,0:15:44.01,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Sorry...{\r}\NS..sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.16,0:15:48.27,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Itsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.96,0:15:54.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone!\NDon't bother me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.78,0:15:56.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you say so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.84,0:16:09.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It was my fault for looking for a car\Nby myself to surprise everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.52,0:16:13.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That explains why it was\Nso cheap for an Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:16.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I got so excited without knowing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.00,0:16:18.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so embarrassed I could die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.89,0:16:22.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're laughing inside, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.53,0:16:23.85,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.45,0:16:28.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... envious of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.83,0:16:30.05,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Envious?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.53,0:16:32.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that BS!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.29,0:16:34.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not BS.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:39.67,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still in high school\Nand you have your own car.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.67,0:16:41.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,My own car?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.62,0:16:44.71,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.  What's wrong with an Eight-Five?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.71,0:16:48.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got an engine, tires and it runs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.18,0:16:51.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it doesn't have power,\Nit can pick up speed on the downhill...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.47,0:16:54.36,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you practice hard\Nand learn some techniques?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.53,0:17:04.43,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Cars are interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.43,0:17:07.03,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, you've changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.03,0:17:08.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Have I?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.28,0:17:11.63,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you were uninterested\Nin cars before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.08,0:17:17.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi, I feel like I could\Nlike my Eight-Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.75,0:17:20.62,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not that good anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:21.81,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.78,0:17:25.69,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't agree so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.46,0:17:30.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better drive on Mt. Akina tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.33,0:17:31.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.89,0:17:35.13,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.  With your Eight-Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.13,0:17:36.92,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.40,0:17:41.66,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pick you up around 10:00pm!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:42.72,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.72,0:17:43.26,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.26,0:17:45.41,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go to bed, just wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.18,0:17:54.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't see the Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.87,0:17:57.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:18:01.05,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to imagine that an\NEight-Six defeated a 32.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.43,0:18:20.96,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that an Eight-Six?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.96,0:18:22.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.57,0:18:28.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, it's so fun driving\Nthe mountain pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.65,0:18:30.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's slow on the straightaways...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:33.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...but it runs well in the corners,\Ndoesn't it, Takumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.52,0:18:34.45,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, more or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.78,0:18:43.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.75,0:18:49.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if I look at it from a distance...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.33,0:18:52.77,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...my Levin looks cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.29,0:18:56.96,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you so cool, my Levin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.96,0:18:59.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I bought this Levin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.12,0:19:03.56,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How optimistic you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.80,0:19:08.41,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,They're just brats.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.41,0:19:10.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,They couldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.20,0:19:14.96,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The technician who defeated\Nthe 32 couldn't be one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:15.86,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.79,0:19:20.80,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How old are you?\NDo you have a license?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.80,0:19:23.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't, you'll be in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.40,0:19:24.51,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I...I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:27.40,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I look young, but I'm eighteen years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.40,0:19:30.14,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}What's with them?\NThey're so rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.59,0:19:32.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point of picking on a child?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.49,0:19:38.69,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like young Road Racer\Nwannabes driving Eight-Sixes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.69,0:19:40.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a local, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.28,0:19:43.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We came here to see the famous Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.28,0:19:44.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.53,0:19:49.48,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a mouth?\NYou know about it, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.48,0:19:53.56,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...I know about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.56,0:19:56.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't think it will\Nshow up tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.53,0:19:59.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That sucks.  And after we\Ncame all the way up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.23,0:20:00.46,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:07.59,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're trying to be a Road Racer,\Ntry not to be so pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.59,0:20:09.76,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with this Eight-Six?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.76,0:20:14.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,These normal wheels make me\Nsick just looking at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.19,0:20:17.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.60,0:20:21.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,At least change the muffler.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.15,0:20:21.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds so uncool.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:25.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know anything\Nabout an Eight-Six?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:30.48,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not an Eight-Six,\Nit's an Eight-Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.48,0:20:34.21,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So even if I changed the muffler,\Nit won't sound good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.21,0:20:36.67,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I still want to change it though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.67,0:20:38.31,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Eight-Five?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.79,0:20:44.51,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you want to change\Nthe muffler...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.51,0:20:48.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...you won't find one anywhere\Nthat fits the Eight-Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.04,0:20:49.77,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,None, anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.77,0:20:51.16,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,My eyes are watering!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.16,0:20:54.68,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen anyone\Ndriving an Eight-Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.68,0:20:57.44,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,A brat deserves an Eight-Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.19,0:21:00.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.35,0:21:02.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I laughed so hard I cried.
